{"tid":1712384,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"沙田大圍大埔各手足向馬上趕往中大解困","createTime":"2019-11-12T14:12:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T14:34:38.000Z","uid":237568,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3e89878ca774b02598020939a45cf39008a793c3","tid":1712384,"uid":237568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:12:23.000Z","msg":"步行又踩單車又好<br />\n去左先<br />\n唇寒齒亡<br />\n中大失守=8大失守<br />\n香港正式淪陷"},{"pid":"34c0f1808d509b4b7aa1f1d7c6abd9d308da65e9","tid":1712384,"uid":237568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:12:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"544d2f16243bfcc94f8d888d7d7dfff3f7409f11","tid":1712384,"uid":261339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:13:18.000Z","msg":"水炮車到橋口冇得轉彎再燒車"},{"pid":"ce1d50742c118dd98ce349fed34fd64a4cbfb779","tid":1712384,"uid":237568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:14:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9b6f235a65e1b933c1825a6b3e7e261ef7ba8aaf","tid":1712384,"uid":237568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:14:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"049eb004e35db72e97cced7b4f8d0aa6bb1a7661","tid":1712384,"uid":237568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:15:11.000Z","msg":"請所有未訓手足盡快增援"},{"pid":"d9d89b608df8fc65579eed429790310cea320370","tid":1712384,"uid":237568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:15:29.000Z","msg":"請所有未訓手足盡快增援"},{"pid":"9a194cb3e37d262f9b2830f377ccc90833000c64","tid":1712384,"uid":237568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:15:44.000Z","msg":"今日失中大 明日失香港"},{"pid":"26ae06573dbd89748c285709d33841d406688cf6","tid":1712384,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:16:09.000Z","msg":"遠水不能救近火！！只係各地開花，班狗可以用無警時份唔理你！！<br />\n<br />\n分頭行事！<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">主力反包！<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">擋水炮車！！</span><br />\n另小隊開花！嘗試分散警力！做得幾多得幾多</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n中大地理難去，但去到就去！人多就咩都有可能！求下大家！！"},{"pid":"a3a00e094f7f31a05fee903932a28b91deacf064","tid":1712384,"uid":32588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:16:12.000Z","msg":"有無集合地點？<br />\n落單好危險"},{"pid":"b0ad57b414bab961d30785908c94c8989ff76e34","tid":1712384,"uid":237568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:16:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XaA2Pe3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXaA2Pe3.jpg&h=edeb7dd7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3e8a0d3bde21876f9283b15fe963922ad3e0f378","tid":1712384,"uid":237568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a3a00e094f7f31a05fee903932a28b91deacf064","tid":1712384,"uid":32588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:16:12.000Z","msg":"有無集合地點？<br />\n落單好危險"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:17:00.000Z","msg":"新城市"},{"pid":"5488dd693393f871de8870ab599bfe140c2cda72","tid":1712384,"uid":237568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:17:16.000Z","msg":"Forward post: <br />\n<br />\n中大人致所有手足 :<br />\n<br />\n談判失敗 我地宣布<br />\n我地全香港人 <br />\n會 進 一 步 行 動 升 級<br />\n我地已經堅持咗兩日<br />\n原本以為已經講好咗黑警會撤退<br />\n呃完我地又再推進 不停開槍<br />\n我地被包圍去到呢個階段<br />\n我 地 已 經 冇 嘢 可 以 輸 <br />\n就算見到真槍都唔會覺得驚<br />\n就 算 犧 牲 都 要 抗 爭 到 底<br />\n<br />\n一 命 換 一 百 黑 警 命<br />\n今晚外圍係一場快閃進攻 <br />\n帶齊燃料 工具 <br />\n著便服扮到無可疑 <br />\n行走期間十字路口放哨<br />\n只要有狗要經過 有天橋高位<br />\n盡一切可能反擊 務求外圍都做到嘢 <br />\n掟 黑 警 氣 油 彈<br />\n掟完 混入返人羣<br />\n香港人 報仇<br />\n入面好多前線手足俾狗圍<br />\n有外來增援亦有同校生<br />\n我地好似噚日咁外圍燒返轉頭<br />\n希望中大外圍都同時開花 <br />\n所有狗車行唔到 冇增援到<br />\n<br />\n落油 起火 拆地盤料 起磚 起樹<br />\n落針 爆玻璃 製造一切混亂<br />\n唔好停 <br />\n推爛所有嘢 務求營救中大生<br />\n<br />\n今日嘅營救 得以聽日繼續同行<br />\n並肩作戰 煲底相見<br />\n<br />\n今日大家用盡一切手段 反攻黑警"},{"pid":"9ad028a8dfc6d6fed7bb0a0089e6d08782c79904","tid":1712384,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:17:25.000Z","msg":"你去左未"},{"pid":"7b0d2b1d00fe5960a81b36cd648192a9ed737538","tid":1712384,"uid":73803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:19:29.000Z","msg":"好塞車，係第一城塞左成個鐘<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64ad8b7f7812c7f6f49de203568e1e342c2e4950","tid":1712384,"uid":63206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:29:27.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"809daaff0ce468384894fbf23e7486ec6d5ba1d2","tid":1712384,"uid":237568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ad028a8dfc6d6fed7bb0a0089e6d08782c79904","tid":1712384,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:17:25.000Z","msg":"你去左未"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:34:17.000Z","msg":"去緊"},{"pid":"173080556ad5d85e615b2dbc7ba24d8647a932fb","tid":1712384,"uid":237568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:34:38.000Z","msg":"推"}]}